---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout>
	<main class="app-container pt-36">
		<h1 class="text-6xl pb-2 font-bold">About Me</h1>
	</main>
	<section class="app-container py-12 mb-8">
		<div
			class="prose prose-neutral prose-lg md:prose-xl dark:prose-invert prose-img:rounded-xl prose-figure:text-center prose-img:mx-auto"
		>
			<p>
				My name is <strong>Uthman Shamim</strong>. I am a student and a <mark
					>Quran reciter.</mark
				> I am currently memorizing the Quran and learning it's meaning from Usstad
				Zakaria Mahmud <i>(Rahimahullah)</i>.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am also learning Arabic, improving my English, and self-studying the
				books of <strong>Madani Nisab</strong>. I am very interested in gaining <strong>Islamic</strong>, Scientific and Historical knowledge, as well as other fields of
				learning. I want to become a knowledgeable <mark>Scholar </mark>in
				future. A Scholar like Sheikh Abdul Majid, Ustad Zakaria Mahmud, and
				Sheikh Saleh Al-Luhaidan <i>(Rahimahullah)</i>.
			</p>
			<p>
				My hobbies include reading and writing. I like to spend my time in reading,
				writing, <strong>Memorizing the Quran</strong>, and learning new things.
				I believe in hard work, patience, and sincerity.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am also interested in programming and technology. I have some
				experience in web development and I am learning new programming
				languages and frameworks too. I wanna use technology to benefit others
				and to spread knowledge.

				<p>
					And at the end my goal is to <mark>Serve Islam</mark> and the world, and to become
					a better Muslim by improving my knowledge day by day.
				</p>
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
